{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260428/s00024/0da307057e3b4f25ba7806634073abed.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">\n    <p>北京玉淵潭公園的紫藤近日進入一年一度的盛花期，園內200多株、15個品種的多花紫藤爭相綻放，遊客可欣賞到多種顏色搭配、繁花如瀑的壯麗景象。</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-28T02:27:22.488399+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":69,"images":1,"source":"明報 消閒","fallback":"none"}}